(The history of artificial intelligence began in antiquity, with myths and stories of artificial) Tj
T* (beings endowed with intelligence. The seeds of modern AI were planted by philosophers) Tj
T* (who attempted to describe the process of human thinking as the mechanical manipulation) Tj
T* (of symbols. This work culminated in the invention of the programmable digital computer in) Tj
T* (the 1940s, a machine based on the abstract essence of mathematical reasoning.) Tj
