(The field of AI research was founded at a workshop held on the campus of Dartmouth) Tj
T* (College during the summer of 1956. Those who attended would become the leaders of AI) Tj
T* (research for decades. Many of them predicted that a machine as intelligent as a human) Tj
T* (being would exist in no more than a generation, and they were given millions of dollars to) Tj
T* (make this vision come true.) Tj
