(Investment and interest in AI boomed in the first decades of the 21st century when) Tj
T* (machine learning was successfully applied to many problems in academia and industry due) Tj
T* (to the availability of large amounts of data and faster computers. The application of artificial) Tj
T* (neural networks to natural language processing enabled significant advances in machine) Tj
T* (translation, text generation, and sentiment analysis.) Tj
