(The ethical implications of artificial intelligence continue to be debated. Concerns include) Tj
T* (the potential for job displacement, algorithmic bias, privacy violations, and the) Tj
T* (concentration of power. Researchers and policymakers are working to develop frameworks) Tj
T* (for responsible AI development that balance innovation with safeguards for human welfare.) Tj
