(Natural language processing has emerged as one of the most impactful subfields of) Tj
T* (artificial intelligence. Early approaches relied on hand-crafted rules and pattern matching.) Tj
T* (Statistical methods introduced in the 1990s improved accuracy significantly by learning) Tj
T* (patterns from large text corpora. The transformer architecture, introduced in 2017,) Tj
T* (revolutionized the field by enabling models to process entire sequences in parallel.) Tj
ET
