(Computer vision is another major area of AI research. The ability of machines to interpret) Tj
T* (and understand visual information from the world has applications ranging from medical) Tj
T* (imaging to autonomous navigation. Convolutional neural networks, first applied) Tj
T* (successfully to image classification in the early 2010s, remain a cornerstone of modern) Tj
T* (computer vision systems.) Tj
ET
