(Reinforcement learning enables AI agents to learn optimal behavior through trial and error.) Tj
T* (An agent interacts with an environment, receiving rewards or penalties for its actions, and) Tj
T* (gradually develops strategies to maximize cumulative reward. This approach has achieved) Tj
T* (remarkable results in game playing, robotics, and resource optimization.) Tj
ET
