(Transfer learning has become a fundamental technique in modern machine learning.) Tj
T* (Rather than training models from scratch for each new task, practitioners can fine-tune) Tj
T* (models that have been pre-trained on large datasets. This approach dramatically reduces) Tj
T* (the amount of task-specific data and computation required, making advanced AI) Tj
T* (capabilities accessible to a wider range of applications and organizations.) Tj
